HEADWORD: Assident
<hw>As"si*dent</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>assidens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>assid⟦emac⟧re</ets> to sit by: cf.
